<tr><td colspan="2" class="MsgR3">
<span class="MsgBodyText">Hi joneo,<br />
<br />
InputStream.read() will block your thread when there is no data <br />
available from the stream and the end of the stream has not been reached.<br />
<br />
I guess that this is the reason for your problem.<br />
<br />
greetings,<br />
Hans<br />
<br />
joneo schrieb:<br />
&gt; hi all,<br />
